Our scaling analysis employs the macroscopic entropy ($S$) ansatz

text:
\begin{equation}

\begin{split}
{\langle N_\mathrm{ch} \rangle} = \left[ b_{\mathrm{{\langle N_\mathrm{ch} \rangle}}} + m_{\mathrm{{\langle N_\mathrm{ch} \rangle}}} \log(\kappa_n {\sqrt{s}}) \right]^3, \\
b_{\mathrm{{\langle N_\mathrm{ch} \rangle}}} = 1.22 \pm 0.01,\  m_{\mathrm{{\langle N_\mathrm{ch} \rangle}}}= 0.775 \pm 0.006, 
\end{split}

\label{eq2}
\end{equation}
